00:10:37,797 --> 00:10:40,432
No. Maybe his, like, nerdy
younger brother.

265
00:10:40,466 --> 00:10:46,071
<i>♪ </i>

266
00:10:46,105 --> 00:10:47,839
Who the hell are you?

267
00:10:50,042 --> 00:10:52,010
