276
00:11:17,069 --> 00:11:19,905
Ten hours after that.

277
00:11:21,741 --> 00:11:24,109
I-I found those jewels in a dumpster.

278
00:11:24,143 --> 00:11:27,813
DeVante, stop lying.

279
00:11:27,847 --> 00:11:30,882
