282
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:35,987
You got the wrong black man.

283
00:11:36,022 --> 00:11:37,389
Okay, who's the right one?

284
00:11:37,423 --> 00:11:39,224
'Cause we got witnesses that
say they saw you

285
00:11:39,258 --> 00:11:40,959
and another guy outside that man's house

286
00:11:40,993 --> 00:11:42,093
right before that happened.

287
00:11:42,128 --> 00:11:43,395
I never went inside.

288
00:11:43,429 --> 00:11:45,297
- Hmm.
- Hmm, so you were there?

289
00:11:45,331 --> 00:11:47,833
No, I didn't say that.
Y'all trying to trip me up.

290
00:11:47,867 --> 00:11:52,204
Okay, let's talk about
your cousin, Andre Griffin.

291
00:11:53,306 --> 00:11:54,472
What about him?

