00:11:54,507 --> 00:11:57,008
Hoffman was Andre's lawyer.

293
00:11:57,043 --> 00:11:59,411
Is that the dead dude's name?

294
00:11:59,445 --> 00:12:01,313
Was Andre with you?

295
00:12:01,347 --> 00:12:04,316
<i>[OMINOUS MUSIC]</i>

296
00:12:04,350 --> 00:12:06,418
Is he the other man our witness saw?

297
00:12:08,988 --> 00:12:13,258
DeVante, you gotta come clean.

298
00:12:14,894 --> 00:12:16,962
Sarge, I got something.

299
00:12:16,996 --> 00:12:19,097
It's important.

300
00:12:19,131 --> 00:12:26,104
<i>♪ </i>

301
00:12:26,138 --> 00:12:28,540
So, this is from a CTA
bus cam last night.

302
00:12:28,574 --> 00:12:30,175
The route goes right past
Hoffman's house.

303
00:12:30,209 --> 00:12:32,177
This was taken at 9:42.

304
00:12:32,211 --> 00:12:39,150
<i>♪ </i>

305
00:12:39,185 --> 00:12:40,819
That's Brian Kelton.

306
00:12:40,853 --> 00:12:43,371
He said he last saw Bernie
at the fundraiser.

307
00:12:44,247 --> 00:12:46,499
So, he lied right to our faces.

308
00:12:47,026 --> 00:12:48,493
Why?

309
00:12:48,527 --> 00:12:54,833
<i>♪ </i>

310
00:12:57,832 --> 00:13:00,767
Under my administration
you're going to see

311
00:13:01,180 --> 00:13:02,769
more police on the street,

312
00:13:02,803 --> 00:13:05,571
more arrests of violent gang members,

313
00:13:05,606 --> 00:13:08,054
more homicides solved,

314
00:13:08,088 --> 00:13:12,168
and your neighborhoods
are going to be safe again.

315
00:13:12,202 --> 00:13:15,453
And I understand I have a long road ahead

316
00:13:15,478 --> 00:13:17,446
before I can gain your trust.

317
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:19,915
We can do better.

318
00:13:19,950 --> 00:13:24,787
But under my leadership,
police reform is working.

319
00:13:25,822 --> 00:13:28,557
And to keep Chicago pointed
in the right direction...

320
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:32,361
I need your help at the ballot box.

321
00:13:32,395 --> 00:13:34,630
You wanna help us?
Stop murdering our children.

322
00:13:34,664 --> 00:13:35,865
ALL: Yeah.

