00:13:35,899 --> 00:13:37,499
- Yeah.
- That's right.

324
00:13:37,534 --> 00:13:38,634
- Yeah.
- Yeah.

325
00:13:38,668 --> 00:13:41,103
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

