00:14:02,525 --> 00:14:05,494
<i>[DRAMATIC MUSIC]</i>

338
00:14:05,528 --> 00:14:07,897
<i>♪ </i>

339
00:14:07,931 --> 00:14:10,065
I was in there, Hank.

340
00:14:10,100 --> 00:14:11,533
Okay.

