00:14:11,568 --> 00:14:12,835
I stopped by for a few minutes.

342
00:14:12,869 --> 00:14:15,337
- Uh-huh.
- I was gone by 9:30.

343
00:14:15,372 --> 00:14:16,839
If I saw or knew anything relevant,

344
00:14:16,873 --> 00:14:19,141
I'd have mentioned it to you.

345
00:14:19,175 --> 00:14:21,427
That's a hell of an omission.

346
00:14:22,445 --> 00:14:24,013
Look, I'm not looking to bury anyone,

347
00:14:24,047 --> 00:14:25,514
I'm just working the case.

348
00:14:25,548 --> 00:14:29,518
<i>♪ </i>

349
00:14:29,552 --> 00:14:33,522
Well, we know that Hoffman
was shot with a 9-millimeter,

