354
00:14:47,437 --> 00:14:49,038
I'll make sure somebody gets it to you.

355
00:14:49,072 --> 00:14:54,043
Bernie... was working on
a personal matter for me.

356
00:14:55,745 --> 00:14:57,746
It's none of my business.

357
00:14:57,781 --> 00:14:59,181
Let's keep it that way.

358
00:14:59,215 --> 00:15:01,884
- We're ready to go, sir.
- Good.

359
00:15:01,918 --> 00:15:03,686
- Sergeant.
- Superintendent.

360
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:05,120
Thanks for the update.

361
00:15:05,155 --> 00:15:12,061
<i>♪ </i>

362
00:15:16,357 --> 00:15:17,733
How'd it go with Kelton?

363
00:15:17,767 --> 00:15:20,069
Admits he was there,
let's see what his gun says.

364
00:15:20,103 --> 00:15:21,804
Sarge, I talked to Cook County jail.

365
00:15:21,838 --> 00:15:23,405
I got some potential DeVante leverage.

