399
00:16:54,830 --> 00:16:56,665
He went there to pick up
something from that white guy.

400
00:16:56,699 --> 00:16:58,834
Okay, what was he picking up,
money, drugs?

401
00:16:58,868 --> 00:17:00,378
I don't know.

402
00:17:00,904 --> 00:17:02,971
All I know is Griff caught the guy

403
00:17:03,006 --> 00:17:04,907
